Extract_Definition.DefinitionDescription: HCM_I040 - HR to Sunlife Feed - Outbound Interface

Block_Criteria.Criteria:
paaf.LEGISLATION_CODE = 'CA' AND paaf.ASSIGNMENT_TYPE = 'E' AND ppos.DATE_START = (select MAX(DATE_START) FROM PER_PERIODS_OF_SERVICE WHERE PERSON_ID = paaf.PERSON_ID AND PERIOD_TYPE = 'E' and DATE_START <= pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE'))
AND (paaf.ASSIGNMENT_STATUS_TYPE_ID IN (SELECT ASSIGNMENT_STATUS_TYPE_ID FROM PER_ASSIGNMENT_STATUS_TYPES_VL WHERE (PER_SYSTEM_STATUS IN ('ACTIVE','SUSPENDED') OR USER_STATUS = 'Inactive - Payroll Eligible'))
OR (ppos.ACTUAL_TERMINATION_DATE >= (pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE')-pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('TERMINATION_DAYS_FLOOR'))))
/*Include AXE Only Employees*/ AND EXISTS ( SELECT 'x' FROM hr_legal_entities hle WHERE hle.organization_id = paaf.legal_entity_id AND status = 'A' AND classification_code = 'HCM_LEMP' AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN hle.effective_start_date AND hle.effective_end_date AND hle.organization_code IN (SELECT hl.lookup_code FROM hcm_lookups hl WHERE enabled_flag = 'Y' AND lookup_type = 'AXE_HR_ANIXTER_LEGAL_EMP_LKP' ) )

Extract_DataElement.BaseGroupName: Assignment Payroll Information Payroll Term Id

Block_Criteria.Criteria: target.INFORMATION_TYPE = 'AXE_CA_PENS_OVRRD_DT' and target.effective_start_date = (select max(target1.effective_start_date) from PER_PEOPLE_EXTRA_INFO_F target1 where target1.person_id = target.person_id and target1.information_type=target.information_type and target1.effective_start_date <=pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE') ) and target.PEI_INFORMATION1='Active'

pauf.address_type = 'HOME' AND paf.address_id = (select papf.MAILING_ADDRESS_ID from per_all_people_f papf where papf.person_id=pauf.person_id and pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE') BETWEEN papf.effective_start_date AND papf.effective_end_date)

Block_Criteria.Criteria:
ET.base_element_name LIKE 'AXE%Bonus%Target%' AND PIV.BASE_NAME = 'Amount'
AND ee.effective_start_date = (select max(ee1.effective_start_date) FROM pay_element_entries_f ee1 where ee1.person_id = ee.person_id and ee1.effective_start_date <= pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE') AND ee1.element_type_id = et.element_type_id)
